            <title>[HBASE-15867] Move HBase replication tracking from ZooKeeper to HBase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-15867</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Move the WAL file and offset tracking out of ZooKeeper and into an HBase table called hbase:replication. &lt;br/&gt;
The largest three new changes will be two classes ReplicationTableBase, TableBasedReplicationQueues, and TableBasedReplicationQueuesClient. As of now ReplicationPeers and HFileRef&apos;s tracking will not be implemented. Subtasks have been filed for these two jobs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
